casebody.data:
ROBINSON
v.
FENDER 2019-1032 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 30, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On appellant's memorandum in support of jurisdiction. This cause originated in the court of appeals and should proceed as an appeal of right pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. 5.01. The clerk shall issue an order for the transmission of the record from the Court of Appeals for Ashtabula County, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07.
